{"word":"Ziklag","slug":"ziklag","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ziklag</b> <a href=\"#/H6860\">H6860</a> <br/> A city within the territory allotted to the tribe of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=31'>Jos 15:31</a><br/> Re-allotted to the tribe of Simeon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=5'>Jos 19:5</a><br/> David dwells at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=6'>1Sa 27:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=1'>2Sa 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=1'>1Ch 12:1</a><br/> Amalekites destroy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30'>1Sa 30</a><br/> Inhabited by the returned exiles of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=28'>Neh 11:28</a>"}]}